184
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,570
I'll know after checking them.

185
00:15:00,410 --> 00:15:01,210
Let's go.

186
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:07,880
Keep up.

187
00:15:08,420 --> 00:15:10,050
