189
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:15,820
Mr. Zhuo.

190
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:17,680
Go wait for me in the mortuary.

191
00:15:17,830 --> 00:15:19,020
Don't worry.

192
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,240
