199
00:15:58,830 --> 00:16:00,000
I can't do

200
00:16:00,030 --> 00:16:01,070
the autopsy.

201
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:03,740
The same thing.

202
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:04,860
The same thing?

203
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:06,630
Not at all!

204
00:16:06,710 --> 00:16:07,830
You're good at shooting.

205
00:16:07,830 --> 00:16:09,310
