214
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:42,760
Sure.

215
00:16:43,290 --> 00:16:45,420
But you'll lose your head in five days.

216
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:48,550
In five days,

217
00:16:48,550 --> 00:16:50,500
I'll go to Mr. Zhuo to resign.

218
